lliurex-auto-upgrade (0.31.5) noble; urgency=medium

  * Merge with upstream:
    * lliurex-auto-upgrade now supports arguments: serve, reload, system-tags,
    remote-tags, dry-run
    * Fixed first random sleep (it was 1, back to 30 seconds) 
    * Removed testing code in dry-run
    * Writting installed packages to
    /run/lliurex-auto-upgrade/installed_packages.log 
    * Added systemd notification when a fist run try fails
    * Service now supports 3 tag paths:
     - /etc/lliurex-auto-upgrade/tags
     - /usr/share/lliurex-auto-upgrade/tags
     - /run/lliurex-auto-upgrade/tags 
    * fixed print_system_info paths
    * Added bash completion file 
    * Added add-tag and delete-tag options  

